value.name: rnyt
value.author: Terence Bonhomme
value.description: Take notes on a Youtube video.

manifest.name: Callout Rem
manifest.author: Min-Ki Park
manifest.description: Decorate your important rem texts with a simple but aesthetic box!

manifest.name: Run JS
manifest.author: Min-Ki Park
manifest.description: Test your JavaScript code snippets within the RemNote environment with ease

manifest.author: Min-Ki Park
manifest.name: Rem Tree
manifest.description: Structure your thoughts easily with Rem Tree!

manifest.name: Puppy Reinforcement
manifest.author: RemNote
manifest.description: Shows motivational dog pics in the queue.

manifest.name: Tabs
manifest.author: RemNote
manifest.description: Organize your knowledgebase with workspaces and tabs.

manifest.name: Statistics
manifest.author: henrik
manifest.description: Statistics plugin that will give you some helpful numbers, charts and heatmap for your knowledge base.

manifest.name: Rainbow Headers
manifest.author: Anisha
manifest.description: Allows you to add color to your headers, and gives you 3 additional header sizes to work with.

manifest.name: Presentation Mode
manifest.author: remnote
manifest.description: Give presentations directly from your notes in RemNote

manifest.name: Minimal Clozes
manifest.author: Anisha
manifest.description: Modifies the appearance of your clozes to make them appear just a little less obtrusive.

manifest.name: Catppuccin: Latte, Frapp, Macciato, and Mocha
manifest.author: coldenate, justTOBBI, and Catppuccin
manifest.description: A soothing pastel theme for your RemNote experience!

manifest.name: Window Manager
manifest.author: Jamesb
manifest.description: Advanced window manager functions.

manifest.name: Cloze Hints
manifest.author: Jamesb
manifest.description: Add hints to clozes

manifest.name: Divider
manifest.author: Min-Ki Park
manifest.description: A Rem for Dividing Paragraphs into Segments

manifest.name: Table of Contents
manifest.description: The RemNote plugin that will create a table of contents from a note.
manifest.author: plant

manifest.name: Object Oriented Noting
manifest.author: 0x00114514
manifest.description: The implementation of some reserved words from OOP languages like Java and C#

manifest.name: RemCord | RemNote Discord RPC
manifest.author: coldenate
manifest.description: Customizable Discord Rich Presence Connection for RemNote. Works everywhere!

manifest.name: Rem to Speech
manifest.author: Mrcoding
manifest.description: Adds text to speech to your current Rem

manifest.name: Random Shuffle Rems
manifest.author: HalfwayDead
manifest.description: Allows you to shuffle children of a Rem in a random order, just like the base app supports for alphabetical order.

manifest.name: Build a Theme
manifest.author: coldenate
manifest.description: [PreRelease]  Build your own theme for RemNote. No Coding Required!

manifest.name: Ease of Sight
manifest.author: mzguntalan
manifest.description: Ease of Sight helps you keep track of what you are reading and/or writing using strategic highlight background colors.

manifest.name: Active Recall in Editor
manifest.author: Min-Ki Park
manifest.description: Utilize the outliner to actively recall and reinforce the information you've learned

manifest.name: Excalidraw
manifest.author: KelongShi
manifest.description: support excalidraw integration

manifest.name: Colorful Answer Button
manifest.author: Min-Ki Park
manifest.description: Colorize your Buttons in Flashcard!
